message.body: Hey Hunter. I can afford to pay you! Are you still able?
I can do it. Do you have the materials?
Cool! I can get them by tomorrow?
I'm going to home depot. I'll let you know when we get them and I can just drop it off.
I'm working on a few things so I might not get to it til this weekend, but bring the materials tomorrow morning if you can
Hmmmm I'm at the mercy of Virginia, who does nothing in the am. Can I just leave stuff on your porch w a note on it?
We'll just drop them off as soon as you are able
Will do. Thanks Hunter! I'll double check my measurements n stuff before you start. And I'm at least going to give Lindsay some free soap ya dirtball!
